Bella Bacino's, the restaurant on the ground floor, offered excellent Chicago-style pizza and interesting beers on tap.	There is an Italian themed restaurant : Bacino's : just outside the foyer that serves as a hotel restaurant.	We did not eat at the restaurant, but there are many nearby, including Dunkin' Donuts and Starbucks for coffee and breakfast.	The hotel restaurant is surprisingly good, and makes the famous Chicago deep dish pizza.